import React from "react";



export const AddForm = ()=>{
    return <form action="" id = 'product_form'>
            <label htmlFor="SKU">SKU</label>
            <input className="form-control" id ='SKU' type="text"placeholder="SKU" />
            <label htmlFor="name">Product Name</label>
            <input className="form-control" id ='name' type="text"placeholder="Product Name" />
            <label   htmlFor="price">Price ($)</label>
            <input  className="form-control" id ='price' type="number"placeholder="Price ($)" />
            <select name="languages" id="productType">
                <option value="javascript">JavaScript</option>
                <option value="DVD">DVD</option>
                <option value="Book">Book</option>
                <option value="Furniture">Furniture</option>
             </select>
      

            
            </form>
}
